  <num>7-1204.02</num>
  <heading>Civil commitment proceedings.</heading>
  <text>Mental health information may be disclosed by a mental health professional when and to the extent necessary to initiate or seek civil commitment proceedings under § <cite path="§21-541">21-541</cite>.</text>
